text: George Breed was a fencer from USA. Breed competed at the 1912 and 1924 Summer Olympics. He was born on 14 July 1876 and died on 24 June 1956.George Breed == References == Category:1876 births Category:1956 deaths Category:American fencers Category:Olympians for the United States Category:Sportspeople from Louisville, Kentucky
